https://privacy.microsoft.com/en-us/privacystatement
Nintendo:
https://www.nintendo.com/us/privacy-policy/
Advertising
We use the following advertising networks to serve ads in our Plague Inc. app on android.. Restricted versions are used to ensure that only contextual ads are shown and personal data processing is limited.
Unity:
https://unity.com/legal/privacy-policy
Admob:
https://policies.google.com/privacy/
Applovin:
https://www.applovin.com/privacy/
Ironsource:
https://developers.ironsrc.com/ironsource-mobile/air/ironsource-mobile-privacy-policy/
